quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,236,"Bakkaatu fawaaki on si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on renndude e maЙ“Й“e maa jaЕ‹tanagol Й“e teЕ‹e, dakmitee Й“e:no fawii galo on yeru makko, no fawii kadi baydoolo on yeru makko.Dakmitirgol Й“e no moЖґЖґiri.Hannduyee fawiiЙ—o moЖґimЙ“e Й“en"
  2,237,"Si on seerii suddiiЙ“e Й“en ado on meemude Й“e, tawa on jaЕ‹tanike Й“e teЕ‹e: ko feccere kon ko jaЕ‹ti-Й—on, si wanaa hara Й“e ya'afi maa on mo dewgal woni e juuЙ—e mu'un ya'afii. Ko nde ya'afotoЙ—on Й“urata Й“aЙ—tinnde gomЙ—al. Wata on yejjitu Й“ural ngal hakkunde mo'on. pellet Alla ko ReenuЙ—o kala ko golloton"
  2,238,"Reenee e julЙ—e Й—en, e julde hakkundeere nden. DaranoЙ—on Alla ko o toЖґЖґiniiЙ“e"
  2,239,"Si on hulii, juulee ko on seppayЙ“e maa waЙ—Й—iiЙ“e. Si on hoolike, jaЕ‹tee Innde Alla nden wano O Anndiniri on kon ko on nganndaano"
  2,240,"ЖЃen maayooЙ“e e mo'on Й“e acca suddiiЙ“e: ko wasiyanagol suddiiЙ“e Й“en dakmitorЙ—um haa hitaande nden timma, ko aldaa e yaltiЕ‹gol Й“e. Si Й“e yaltii, bakkaatu fawaaki on e kon ko Й“e waЙ—ani ko'e maЙ“Й“e e moЖґЖґere. Alla ko FooluЙ—o Г‘eeГ±uЙ—o"
  2,241,"No woodani Й“en seeraaЙ“e: dakamitorgol no moЖґЖґiri. ko goongofawiiЙ—o gomЙ—uЙ“e Й“en"
  2,242,"Ko wano nii Alla ЖЃaЕ‹nginiraЕ‹ta on Aayeeje Makko Й—en, belajo'o on haqqilay"